{"type":"message","id":"a74cfd81","parentId":"95db175d","timestamp":"2026-04-06T12:11:20.469Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"两个端点都能正常工作！所以问题不是 Router 服务本身。\n\n504 错误是 Gateway 的代理返回的。可能油猴脚本发送的请求 URL 有问题。\n\n让我再看看油猴脚本的 API 配置：\n\n```javascript\napiUrl: 'http://localhost:3102/api/task',\n```\n\n这看起来是对的...但是等等，用户遇到的是 504 错误，而这个 504 是 \"Error occurred while trying to proxy\"，说明请求被代理到了某处。\n\n可能的问题：\n1. 用户的浏览器实际上访问的是 3103 端口（油猴匹配规则是 localhost:3103/*），但是油猴脚本发送请求到 3102，这个代理错误可能来自 3103 端口的服务？\n2. 或者有某种网络配置问题？\n\n让我仔细想想...用户的油猴脚本匹配的是 `localhost:3103/*` 和 `127.0.0.1:3103/*`，但请求发送到 `localhost:3102/api/task`。\n\n如果 3103 端口有另一个服务在监听，它可能会尝试代理这个请求？\n\n让我检查 3103 端口：\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d62b44b82280318cc848e1db942e4","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ss -tlnp | grep 3103 || echo \"3103 端口无监听\"","timeout":5}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":4057,"output":271,"cacheRead":14336,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18664,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775477467845,"responseId":"019d62b41f2e8f3bf7052919c4b70806"}}
