{"type":"message","id":"6c9e6d47","parentId":"48f9cd31","timestamp":"2026-04-06T12:11:32.651Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Gateway (18789) 没有运行。这就解释了 504 的原因了！\n\nRouter 的代码是这样的：所有的路由如果没有匹配到，就会被代理到 Gateway (18789)。但 Gateway 没有运行，所以代理失败返回 504。\n\n但为什么 `/api/score` 和 `/api/task` 会走代理？让我再看看代码...\n\n啊！我发现问题了。油猴脚本发送的是 **POST** 请求到 `/api/task`，但是代码里定义的是：\n\n```javascript\napp.post('/api/task', async (req, res) => {...})\n```\n\n这应该能匹配到才对...让我再仔细测试一下 POST 请求。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_fc6344a2c32a489eb59fb935","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s -X POST http://localhost:3102/api/task -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d '{\"taskSpec\":\"test\"}' -w \"\\nHTTP_CODE: %{http_code}\"","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":19087,"output":202,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19289,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775477486779,"responseId":"chatcmpl-a2371f53-0915-46ad-8256-78f195f04005"}}
