{"type":"message","id":"426f1f20","parentId":"747d8553","timestamp":"2026-04-06T12:11:40.097Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"从命令行 curl 请求是完全正常的！返回 200。所以 Router 本身工作正常。油猴脚本遇到 504 的原因可能是：1. 浏览器中的请求被某种代理或扩展拦截\n2. GM_xmlhttpRequest 的某些问题\n\n让我告诉用户 Router 服务正常工作，可能是其他原因导致的。如果用户在浏览器里遇到问题，可以尝试：\n1. 检查浏览器是否有其他代理扩展\n2. 查看油猴脚本的 console 日志\n3. 确认油猴脚本真的在运行\n\n但是等等，用户发送的错误是 `HTTP 504: Error occurred while trying to proxy: localhost:3102/api/score`\n\n注意是 `/api/score` 不是 `/api/task`。可能用户测试了不同的端点，或者油猴脚本有不同版本。\n\n让我再想想...这个错误信息 \"Error occurred while trying to proxy\" 是在请求确实到达了 Router，但 Router 尝试代理到 Gateway (18789) 时失败的。\n\n但我测试的 /api/score 和 /api/task 都没有触发代理，它们直接由 Router 处理了。这很奇怪...\n\n等等，我注意到路由定义：```javascript\napp.get('/api/score', ...)  // GET\napp.post('/api/task', ...)  // POST\n```\n\n如果油猴发送的是 GET 请求到 /api/task 会怎样？没有匹配的路由，就会走到代理。\n\n可能的情况是用户测试了 GET 请求到 /api/score 或者发错了端点。\n\n我的建议是油猴脚本配置的端点没问题，Router 服务正常运行，用户需要检查浏览器控制台的具体错误日志来确认请求是否真的到达了 Router。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nRouter 服务本身正常！从命令行测试都返回 200：\n\n```bash\n# GET /api/score → 200 ✓\n# POST /api/task → 200 ✓\n```\n\n**504 的根因：** Gateway (18789) 端口没有运行。当请求没有匹配到 Router 的内置路由时，会 fallback 走代理到 Gateway，但 Gateway 不可用就返回 504。\n\n**解决方案：**\n\n1. **启动 Gateway：**\n   ```bash\n   openclaw gateway start\n   ```\n\n2. **或者油猴脚本的 `@match` 改正确**（如果你不需要代理 fallback 功能）：\n   - 当前：`@match http://localhost:3103/*` （3103 没服务）\n   - 应该是：`@match http://localhost:3102/*`\n\n你能确认下 Gateway 有没有运行吗？`openclaw gateway status`"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":19353,"output":496,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19849,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775477492695,"responseId":"chatcmpl-037598c5-48dc-40a7-aac2-3f32e6b33c2d"}}
{"type":"message","id":"568b0bef","parentId":"426f1f20","timestamp":"2026-04-06T12:20:13.596Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Mon 2026-04-06 20:20 GMT+8] 重新检查一下，不要做任何事情，先告诉我：// ==UserScript==\n// @name OpenClaw Dynamic Scorer\n// @namespace http://tampermonkey.net/\n// @version 3.0\n// @description 调用动态评分 API，显示真实分数\n// @match http://localhost:3103/*\n// @match http://127.0.0.1:3103/*\n// @grant GM_xmlhttpRequest\n// ==/UserScript==\n\n(function() {\n 'use strict';\n\n // 评分 API 地址（注意是 /api/task）\n const API_URL = 'http://localhost:3102/api/task';\n\n // 创建悬浮按钮\n const btn = document.createElement('button');\n btn.textContent = '📊 动态评分';\n btn.style.cssText = `\n position: fixed; bottom: 20px; right: 20px;\n z-index: 10000; padding: 10px 20px;\n background: #007bff; color: white; border: none;\n border-radius: 40px; font-size: 16px; cursor: pointer;\n box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n `;\n document.body.appendChild(btn);\n\n // 获取当前输入框内容\n function getInputText() {\n const active = document.activeElement;\n if (active && (active.tagName === 'TEXTAREA' || active.isContentEditable)) {\n return active.value || active.innerText;\n }\n const selectors = ['textarea', '[contenteditable=\"true\"]', '.chat-input', 'input'];\n for (let sel of selectors) {\n let el = document.querySelector(sel);\n if (el) return el.value || el.innerText;\n }\n return '';\n }\n\n // 显示结果弹窗\n function showResult(score, plan) {\n const modal = document.createElement('div');\n modal.style.cssText = `position:fixed; top:0; left:0; width:100%; height:100%; background:rgba(0,0,0,0.5); display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; z-index:10001;`;\n modal.innerHTML = `\n <div style=\"background:white; border-radius:12px; padding:20px; max-width:400px;\">\n <h3>📊 动态评分结果</h3>\n <div><strong>总分:</strong> ${score}</div>\n <div><strong>执行模式:</strong> ${plan.mode}</div>\n <div><strong>超时:</strong> ${plan.timeoutSec || plan.stepTimeoutSec} 秒</div>\n <div><strong>内存限制:</strong> ${plan.memLimitMB ? plan.memLimitMB + ' MB' : '无限制'}</div>\n <button id=\"close-modal\" style=\"margin-top:15px;\">关闭</button>\n </div>\n `;\n document.body.appendChild(modal);\n document.getElementById('close-modal').onclick = () => modal.remove();\n modal.onclick = (e) => { if (e.target === modal) modal.remove(); };\n }\n\n btn.onclick = () => {\n const taskSpec = getInputText();\n if (!taskSpec) {\n alert('请先在输入框中输入任务描述');\n return;\n }\n btn.disabled = true;\n btn.textContent = '评分中...';\n GM_xmlhttpRequest({\n method: 'POST',\n url: API_URL,\n headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },\n data: JSON.stringify({ taskSpec }),\n timeout: 5000,\n onload: (resp) => {\n btn.disabled = false;\n btn.textContent = '📊 动态评分';\n if (resp.status === 200) {\n try {\n const data = JSON.parse(resp.responseText);\n showResult(data.score, data.routing);\n } catch(e) {\n alert('解析响应失败');\n }\n } else {\n alert(`评分失败: HTTP ${resp.status}`);\n }\n },\n onerror: (err) => {\n btn.disabled = false;\n btn.textContent = '📊 动态评分';\n alert('请求失败: ' + err.error);\n },\n ontimeout: () => {\n btn.disabled = false;\n btn.textContent = '📊 动态评分';\n alert('请求超时，请确保评分API服务已启动');\n }\n });\n };\n})();"}],"timestamp":1775478013588}}
{"type":"message","id":"e4d0d208","parentId":"568b0bef","timestamp":"2026-04-06T12:20:15.784Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to analyze this Userscript without making any changes. Let me check:\n\n1. `@match http://localhost:3103/*` - but nothing is running on 3103\n2. API calls to `http://localhost:3102/api/task` - this works (I tested it)\n3. The script tries to access localhost:3103 which has no server, so the script won't even load/run on that page\n\nThe issue is clear: the @match points to port 3103, but there's nothing there. The actual API is on 3102.\n\nLet me give a clear analysis.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n**问题分析：**\n\n| 配置项 | 值 | 状态 |\n|--------|-----|------|\n| `@match` | `localhost:3103/*` | ❌ 无服务 |\n| API URL | `localhost:3102/api/task` | ✅ 正常 |\n\n**结论：** 脚本加载的页面（3103）不存在，所以脚本根本不会运行。\n\n油猴脚本需要在 **3102 页面** 上才能生效，但你的 UI 可能在 3103？\n\n**修复方案（2选1）：**\n\n1. **如果 UI 在 3103**：把 API URL 改成完整路径，并确保油猴允许跨域\n2. **如果 UI 在 3102**：把 `@match` 改成 `http://localhost:3102/*`\n\n你想让这个脚本在哪个页面运行？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":19381,"output":292,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19673,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775478013596,"responseId":"chatcmpl-826c8899-0aca-4a1d-bf49-c4272b6c7997"}}
