{"type":"message","id":"42a4eba2","parentId":"e23220ce","timestamp":"2026-04-06T12:24:16.774Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"确实，routing 对象里没有 memLimitMB 字段。这是因为 score=20 时，执行模式是 DIRECT，根据 getExecutionPlan 的逻辑，DIRECT 模式没有设置 memLimitMB。\n\n让我看一下 scoring.js 里的 getExecutionPlan 函数是怎么定义的。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_56e62ba9bcb54c22b7ecc107","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/openclaw-router/scoring.js"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":21503,"output":84,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21587,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775478252467,"responseId":"chatcmpl-61cfc33d-dcb0-437d-90d7-90c0a4acd978"}}
{"type":"message","id":"b30841bd","parentId":"42a4eba2","timestamp":"2026-04-06T12:24:16.799Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_56e62ba9bcb54c22b7ecc107","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"// scoring.js - Task Orchestrator v3.0\n// 评分因子与路由 - 调整后支持 0-100 分完整覆盖\n\nconst WEIGHTS = {\n instructionCount: 0.12,\n codeLines: 0.08,\n dependencyComplexity: 0.10,\n cpuIntensity: 0.10,\n ioIntensity: 0.08,\n networkIntensity: 0.12,\n estimatedDuration: 0.12,\n scaleIndex: 0.28\n};\n\nfunction computeComplexity(taskSpec) {\n const cnt = (taskSpec.match(/&&|;|\\n/g) || []).length + 1;\n if (cnt === 1) return 1;\n if (cnt <= 3) return 2;\n if (cnt <= 6) return 3;\n if (cnt <= 10) return 4;\n return 5;\n}\n\nfunction computeCodeLines(taskSpec) {\n const lines = (taskSpec.match(/\\n/g) || []).length + 1;\n if (lines <= 10) return 1;\n if (lines <= 50) return 2;\n if (lines <= 100) return 3;\n if (lines <= 500) return 4;\n return 5;\n}\n\nfunction computeScaleIndex(taskSpec) {\n const lower = taskSpec.toLowerCase();\n let score = 0;\n \n const patterns = [\n   'docker', 'docker-compose', 'kubernetes', 'kubectl', 'helm',\n   'terraform', 'ansible', 'packer', 'vault',\n   'jenkins', 'gitlab', 'github actions', 'ci cd',\n   'git clone', 'npm install', 'pip install',\n   'make all', 'make test', 'build', 'compile'\n ];\n \n for (const p of patterns) {\n   if (lower.includes(p)) score += 1;\n }\n \n // 基础分1，最多加到5\n return Math.min(5, Math.max(1, score));\n}\n\nasync function computeFineScore(taskSpec) {\n const factors = {\n   instructionCount: computeComplexity(taskSpec),\n   codeLines: computeCodeLines(taskSpec),\n   dependencyComplexity: /npm install|pip install|apt install|yum install|brew install/i.test(taskSpec) ? 4 : \n                          /install|setup|init/i.test(taskSpec) ? 2 : 1,\n   cpuIntensity: /make|compile|gcc|g\\+\\+|clang|build|npm run build/i.test(taskSpec) ? 4 : \n                 /python.*\\.py|node.*\\.js/i.test(taskSpec) ? 2 : 1,\n   ioIntensity: /cp|mv|tar|dd|rsync|backup|dump/i.test(taskSpec) ? 4 : 1,\n   networkIntensity: /curl|wget|git clone|fetch|download|http|https/i.test(taskSpec) ? 4 : \n                     /ssh|scp|rsync/i.test(taskSpec) ? 2 : 1,\n   estimatedDuration: /sleep|wait|timeout/i.test(taskSpec) ? 4 : \n                      /compile|build|install|test/i.test(taskSpec) ? 3 : 1,\n   scaleIndex: computeScaleIndex(taskSpec)\n };\n \n let weighted = 0;\n for (const [k, v] of Object.entries(factors)) {\n   weighted += v * WEIGHTS[k];\n }\n \n const totalScore = Math.min(100, Math.round(weighted * 20));\n return { totalScore, factors };\n}\n\nfunction getExecutionPlan(score, scaleIndex) {\n if (scaleIndex >= 4) return { mode: 'MEGA_TASK', timeoutSec: 7200, memLimitMB: 8192 };\n if (score <= 20) return { mode: 'DIRECT', timeoutSec: 30 };\n if (score <= 40) return { mode: 'STEP_ARCHIVE', stepTimeoutSec: 60, memLimitMB: 1024 };\n if (score <= 60) return { mode: 'SPAWN_SUBAGENT', timeoutSec: Math.max(60, Math.min(180, score * 3)), memLimitMB: 2048 };\n if (score <= 80) return { mode: 'PARALLEL_SHARDS', timeoutSec: Math.max(120, Math.min(160, score * 2)), memLimitMB: 2048 };\n return { mode: 'MEGA_TASK', timeoutSec: 7200, memLimitMB: 8192 };\n}\n\nmodule.exports = { computeFineScore, getExecutionPlan };"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775478256792}}
{"type":"message","id":"792761b2","parentId":"b30841bd","timestamp":"2026-04-06T12:24:34.207Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我看到了问题！看第66-71行：\n\n```javascript\nfunction getExecutionPlan(score, scaleIndex) {\n if (scaleIndex >= 4) return { mode: 'MEGA_TASK', timeoutSec: 7200, memLimitMB: 8192 };\n if (score <= 20) return { mode: 'DIRECT', timeoutSec: 30 };\n if (score <= 40) return { mode: 'STEP_ARCHIVE', stepTimeoutSec: 60, memLimitMB: 1024 };\n if (score <= 60) return { mode: 'SPAWN_SUBAGENT', timeoutSec: Math.max(60, Math.min(180, score * 3)), memLimitMB: 2048 };\n if (score <= 80) return { mode: 'PARALLEL_SHARDS', timeoutSec: Math.max(120, Math.min(160, score * 2)), memLimitMB: 2048 };\n return { mode: 'MEGA_TASK', timeoutSec: 7200, memLimitMB: 8192 };\n}\n```\n\n当 score <= 20 时，是 DIRECT 模式，**没有返回 memLimitMB**。\n\n这是代码逻辑问题：DIRECT 模式没有设置内存限制。应该改成：\n```javascript\nif (score <= 20) return { mode: 'DIRECT', timeoutSec: 30, memLimitMB: 512 };\n```\n\n或者至少返回 null 而不是 undefined。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n找到原因了！看 `scoring.js` 第 67 行：\n\n```javascript\nif (score <= 20) return { mode: 'DIRECT', timeoutSec: 30 };\n//                                            ↑ 没有 memLimitMB\n```\n\n**修复：** 在 Router 代码里给 DIRECT 模式也加上内存限制。\n\n```javascript\nif (score <= 20) return { mode: 'DIRECT', timeoutSec: 30, memLimitMB: 512 };\n```\n\n要我帮你改吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":2514,"output":395,"cacheRead":20096,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":23005,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775478256799,"responseId":"019d62bfa4ce208f2c49c5ba37dbb5ed"}}
