{"type":"message","id":"d4f18273","parentId":"f22f7a92","timestamp":"2026-04-06T12:27:50.071Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019d62c2b3b3a33cc7e32cfb1a0f7962","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"// scoring.js - Task Orchestrator v3.0\n// 评分因子与路由 - 调整后支持 0-100 分完整覆盖\n\nconst WEIGHTS = {\n instructionCount: 0.12,\n codeLines: 0.08,\n dependencyComplexity: 0.10,\n cpuIntensity: 0.10,\n ioIntensity: 0.08,\n networkIntensity: 0.12,\n estimatedDuration: 0.12,\n scaleIndex: 0.28\n};\n\nfunction computeComplexity(taskSpec) {\n const cnt = (taskSpec.match(/&&|;|\\n/g) || []).length + 1;\n if (cnt === 1) return 1;\n if (cnt <= 3) return 2;\n if (cnt <= 6) return 3;\n if (cnt <= 10) return 4;\n return 5;\n}\n\nfunction computeCodeLines(taskSpec) {\n const lines = (taskSpec.match(/\\n/g) || []).length + 1;\n if (lines <= 10) return 1;\n if (lines <= 50) return 2;\n if (lines <= 100) return 3;\n if (lines <= 500) return 4;\n return 5;\n}\n\nfunction computeScaleIndex(taskSpec) {\n const lower = taskSpec.toLowerCase();\n let score = 0;\n \n // 英文关键词\n const enPatterns = [\n   'docker', 'docker-compose', 'kubernetes', 'kubectl', 'helm',\n   'terraform', 'ansible', 'packer', 'vault',\n   'jenkins', 'gitlab', 'github actions', 'ci cd',\n   'git clone', 'npm install', 'pip install', 'yarn install',\n   'make all', 'make test', 'build', 'compile', 'deploy'\n ];\n \n // 中文关键词\n const cnPatterns = [\n   'docker', '容器', 'k8s', 'helm', '部署', '发布',\n   'jenkins', 'ci/cd', '持续集成', 'gitlab', '克隆',\n   '安装依赖', '编译', '构建', '打包', '测试', '单元测试',\n   '迁移', '备份', '同步', '批量', '多文件'\n ];\n \n for (const p of enPatterns) {\n   if (lower.includes(p)) score += 1;\n }\n \n for (const p of cnPatterns) {\n   if (taskSpec.includes(p)) score += 1;\n }\n \n // 基础分1，最多加到5\n return Math.min(5, Math.max(1, score));\n}\n\nasync function computeFineScore(taskSpec) {\n const factors = {\n   instructionCount: computeComplexity(taskSpec),\n   codeLines: computeCodeLines(taskSpec),\n   dependencyComplexity: /npm install|pip install|apt install|yum install|brew install/i.test(taskSpec) ? 4 : \n                          /install|setup|init/i.test(taskSpec) ? 2 : 1,\n   cpuIntensity: /make|compile|gcc|g\\+\\+|clang|build|npm run build/i.test(taskSpec) ? 4 : \n                 /python.*\\.py|node.*\\.js/i.test(taskSpec) ? 2 : 1,\n   ioIntensity: /cp|mv|tar|dd|rsync|backup|dump/i.test(taskSpec) ? 4 : 1,\n   networkIntensity: /curl|wget|git clone|fetch|download|http|https/i.test(taskSpec) ? 4 : \n                     /ssh|scp|rsync/i.test(taskSpec) ? 2 : 1,\n   estimatedDuration: /sleep|wait|timeout/i.test(taskSpec) ? 4 : \n                      /compile|build|install|test/i.test(taskSpec) ? 3 : 1,\n   scaleIndex: computeScaleIndex(taskSpec)\n };\n \n let weighted = 0;\n for (const [k, v] of Object.entries(factors)) {\n   weighted += v * WEIGHTS[k];\n }\n \n const totalScore = Math.min(100, Math.round(weighted * 20));\n return { totalScore, factors };\n}\n\nfunction getExecutionPlan(score, scaleIndex) {\n if (scaleIndex >= 4) return { mode: 'MEGA_TASK', timeoutSec: 7200, memLimitMB: 8192 };\n if (score <= 20) return { mode: 'DIRECT', timeoutSec: 30 };\n if (score <= 40) return { mode: 'STEP_ARCHIVE', stepTimeoutSec: 60, memLimitMB: 1024 };\n if (score <= 60) return { mode: 'SPAWN_SUBAGENT', timeoutSec: Math.max(60, Math.min(180, score * 3)), memLimitMB: 2048 };\n if (score <= 80) return { mode: 'PARALLEL_SHARDS', timeoutSec: Math.max(120, Math.min(160, score * 2)), memLimitMB: 2048 };\n return { mode: 'MEGA_TASK', timeoutSec: 7200, memLimitMB: 8192 };\n}\n\nmodule.exports = { computeFineScore, getExecutionPlan };"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775478470066}}
{"type":"message","id":"604cf82a","parentId":"d4f18273","timestamp":"2026-04-06T12:28:00.027Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see that my changes are there but the scaleIndex is only worth 28% weight. For \"写一个Python脚本处理数据\", let's see what values we get:\n- instructionCount: computeComplexity - there's only 1 line, no && or ; so cnt = 1 → returns 1\n- codeLines: 1 line → computeCodeLines returns 1\n- dependencyComplexity: no install/setup → returns 1\n- cpuIntensity: has \"Python脚本\" → matches /python.*\\.py|node.*\\.js/i → returns 2\n- ioIntensity: no match → 1\n- networkIntensity: no match → 1\n- estimatedDuration: no match → 1\n- scaleIndex: no match in patterns → score = 0 → Math.max(1, 0) = 1\n\nSo factors:\n- instructionCount: 1\n- codeLines: 1\n- dependencyComplexity: 1\n- cpuIntensity: 2\n- ioIntensity: 1\n- networkIntensity: 1\n- estimatedDuration: 1\n- scaleIndex: 1\n\nweighted = 1*0.12 + 1*0.08 + 1*0.10 + 2*0.10 + 1*0.08 + 1*0.12 + 1*0.12 + 1*0.28\n        = 0.12 + 0.08 + 0.10 + 0.20 + 0.08 + 0.12 + 0.12 + 0.28\n        = 1.00\ntotalScore = 1.00 * 20 = 20\n\nSo the score is 20 as expected. The problem is that \"脚本\" (script) isn't in my cnPatterns. Let me add more Chinese keywords to boost the score:\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_618ccc9efc8146868b52a7a4","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"// 中文关键词\n const cnPatterns = [\n   'docker', '容器', 'k8s', 'helm', '部署', '发布',\n   'jenkins', 'ci/cd', '持续集成', 'gitlab', '克隆',\n   '安装依赖', '编译', '构建', '打包', '测试', '单元测试',\n   '迁移', '备份', '同步', '批量', '多文件', '脚本',\n   'api', '接口', '服务器', '前端', '后端', '数据库'\n ];","oldText":"// 中文关键词\n const cnPatterns = [\n   'docker', '容器', 'k8s', 'helm', '部署', '发布',\n   'jenkins', 'ci/cd', '持续集成', 'gitlab', '克隆',\n   '安装依赖', '编译', '构建', '打包', '测试', '单元测试',\n   '迁移', '备份', '同步', '批量', '多文件'\n ];"}],"path":"/home/ai/openclaw-router/scoring.js"}}],"api":"openai