{"type":"message","id":"e9a950ed","parentId":"625b4d5e","timestamp":"2026-04-06T12:33:25.220Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想让我修改当前的 openclaw-router.js，让它返回 factors。\n\n看一下当前的代码：\n```javascript\napp.post('/api/task', async (req, res) => {\n  const taskSpec = req.body?.taskSpec || '';\n  if (taskSpec) {\n    const score = await computeFineScore(taskSpec);\n    const plan = getExecutionPlan(score.totalScore, score.factors?.scaleIndex || 1);\n    console.log(`[Router] Task scored: ${score.totalScore} → ${plan.mode}`);\n    res.json({ \n      taskSpec, \n      score: score.totalScore,\n      routing: plan,\n      message: 'Task scored, ready to execute'\n    });\n  } else {\n    res.status(400).json({ error: 'Missing taskSpec' });\n  }\n});\n```\n\n改成返回 factors 需要改成类似：\n```javascript\nres.json({ \n  taskSpec, \n  score: score.totalScore,\n  routing: plan,\n  factors: score.factors,\n  message: 'Task scored, ready to execute'\n});\n```\n\n让我确认一下用户的问题 - 他问\"可以修改一下让他返回 factors不？先回答我\"\n\n我需要先回答他能否修改。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n可以。改成这样：\n\n```javascript\nres.json({ \n  taskSpec, \n  score: score.totalScore,\n  routing: plan,\n  factors: score.factors,  // 加这行\n  message: 'Task scored, ready to execute'\n});\n```\n\n要我改吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":32396,"output":307,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32703,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775478800341,"responseId":"chatcmpl-4c6c7780-5625-4cec-9079-7b4d135e33e3"}}
