{"type":"message","id":"7211562e","parentId":"ace0821c","timestamp":"2026-04-06T12:34:30.211Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019d62c8ea9fabf912fcc1fbb7d26fd4","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"taskSpec\": \"测试\",\n  \"score\": 25,\n  \"routing\": {\n    \"mode\": \"STEP_ARCHIVE\",\n    \"stepTimeoutSec\": 60,\n    \"memLimitMB\": 1024\n  },\n  \"factors\": {\n    \"instructionCount\": 1,\n    \"codeLines\": 1,\n    \"dependencyComplexity\": 1,\n    \"cpuIntensity\": 1,\n    \"ioIntensity\": 1,\n    \"networkIntensity\": 1,\n    \"estimatedDuration\": 3,\n    \"scaleIndex\": 1\n  },\n  \"message\": \"Task scored, ready to execute\"\n}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":2036,"aggregated":"{\n  \"taskSpec\": \"测试\",\n  \"score\": 25,\n  \"routing\": {\n    \"mode\": \"STEP_ARCHIVE\",\n    \"stepTimeoutSec\": 60,\n    \"memLimitMB\": 1024\n  },\n  \"factors\": {\n    \"instructionCount\": 1,\n    \"codeLines\": 1,\n    \"dependencyComplexity\": 1,\n    \"cpuIntensity\": 1,\n    \"ioIntensity\": 1,\n    \"networkIntensity\": 1,\n    \"estimatedDuration\": 3,\n    \"scaleIndex\": 1\n  },\n  \"message\": \"Task scored, ready to execute\"\n}","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775478870204}}
{"type":"message","id":"a0641f32","parentId":"7211562e","timestamp":"2026-04-06T12:34:31.220Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"已经返回 factors 了。现在可以告诉用户完成了。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n搞定 ✅ 现在返回 `factors` 了。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":33215,"output":22,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33237,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775478870212,"responseId":"chatcmpl-76821673-981f-44f2-bd63-272219002911"}}
{"type":"message","id":"c071b83f","parentId":"a0641f32","timestamp":"2026-04-06T12:35:43.658Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Mon 2026-04-06 20:35 GMT+8] 有这个功能吗？先回答我：// scoring.js - 动态评分（根据命令数量、网络依赖等）\nfunction computeComplexity(taskSpec) {\n const cmdCount = (taskSpec.match(/&&|;|\\n/g) || []).length + 1;\n if (cmdCount === 1) return 1;\n if (cmdCount <= 3) return 3;\n if (cmdCount <= 6) return 4;\n return 5;\n}\n\nfunction computeNetworkIntensity(taskSpec) {\n if (/\\b(curl|wget|npm install|pip install|git clone)\\b/.test(taskSpec)) return 5;\n return 1;\n}\n\nfunction computeEstimatedDuration(taskSpec) {\n if (/\\b(sleep|make|compile|build)\\b/.test(taskSpec)) return 4;\n return 1;\n}\n\nasync function computeFineScore(taskSpec) {\n const factors = {\n instructionCount: computeComplexity(taskSpec),\n networkIntensity: computeNetworkIntensity(taskSpec),\n estimatedDuration: computeEstimatedDuration(taskSpec),\n scaleIndex: 1, // 可扩展\n };\n // 加权总分（满分5+5+5=15，映射到0-100）\n const total = (factors.instructionCount * 0.4 + factors.networkIntensity * 0.3 + factors.estimatedDuration * 0.3);\n const totalScore = Math.min(100, Math.max(0, Math.round(total / 5 * 100)));\n return { totalScore, factors };\n}\n\nfunction getExecutionPlan(score, scaleIndex = 1) {\n if (score <= 20) return { mode: 'DIRECT', timeoutSec: 30, memLimitMB: null };\n if (score <= 40) return { mode: 'STEP_ARCHIVE', stepTimeoutSec: 60, memLimitMB: 1024 };\n if (score <= 60) return { mode: 'SPAWN_SUBAGENT', timeoutSec: Math.max(60, score), memLimitMB: 2048 };\n return { mode: 'MULTI_SUBAGENT', timeoutSec: 300, memLimitMB: 2048 };\n}\n\nmodule.exports = { computeFineScore, getExecutionPlan };"}],"timestamp":1775478943652}}
{"type":"message","id":"16de903a","parentId":"c071b83f","timestamp":"2026-04-06T12:36:02.255Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户在问当前运行的 scoring.js 是否具有这个功能。让我对比一下：\n\n用户提供的新版本有这些特点：\n1. `computeComplexity` - 根据 && ; \\n 计算命令数量，但阈值不同（<=3 返回 3，<=6 返回 4）\n2. `computeNetworkIntensity` - 简单正则检测 curl|wget|npm install|pip install|git clone，返回 5 或 1\n3. `computeEstimatedDuration` - 检测 sleep|make|compile|build，返回 4 或 1\n4. 评分公式简化：`instructionCount * 0.4 + networkIntensity * 0.3 + estimatedDuration * 0.3`，然后映射到 0-100\n5. `getExecutionPlan` 最终模式是 `MULTI_SUBAGENT` 而不是 `MEGA_TASK`\n\n当前运行的 scoring.js 更复杂，有 8 个因子，不同的权重计算方式。\n\n功能上有些类似，但当前的更详细。用户问有没有这个功能 - 不是完全一样，但有类似功能。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n类似，但不是完全一样。\n\n| 对比 | 你的版本 | 当前运行版本 |\n|------|---------|-------------|\n| 因子数量 | 3个 | 8个 |\n| 复杂度计算 | 简单 (&&;\\n) | 相同 + 中文支持 |\n| 网络强度 | 简单正则 | 更细致分级 |\n| 执行模式 | MULTI_SUBAGENT | MEGA_TASK |\n\n当前版本更精细，你的版本更简洁。要替换成你提供的版本吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":1200,"output":307,"cacheRead":32512,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34019,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775478943657,"responseId":"019d62caa47ae356095e7d020024e06c"}}
