{"type":"message","id":"5e935151","parentId":"7f7f2139","timestamp":"2026-04-06T12:50:11.815Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"看到关键日志了：```\nApr 06 20:43:22 ai node[43492]: 2026-04-06T20:43:22.135+08:00 [ws] unauthorized conn=fe736465-38ff-4956-a535-fbd1ee211d9f remote=127.0.0.1 client=openclaw-control-ui webchat vcontrol-ui reason=token_missing\nApr 06 20:43:22 ai node[43492]: 2026-04-06T20:43:22.139+08:00 [ws] closed before connect conn=fe736465-38ff-4956-a535-fbd1ee211d9f remote=127.0.0.1 fwd=n/a origin=http://127.0.0.1:3108 host=127.0.0.1:3108 ua=Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/146.0.0.0 Safari/537.36 Edg/146.0.0.0 code=1008 reason=unauthorized: gateway token missing (open the dashboard URL and paste the token in Control UI settings)\n```\n\n问题是 **token_missing**，不是 token 不匹配。这意味着 ws-proxy 没有正确发送 token。\n\nws-proxy 代码里有硬编码的 token：`'0da4fe1cb845fc8386105026ee6b941b288a2a4264a16ced'`\n\n但这可能不是正确的 token。我需要获取 Gateway 的实际 token。\n \n不过 Gateway 是编译后的二进制，无法直接修改它来添加白名单。我可以尝试从配置文件或环境中读取实际 token，或者看看 OpenClaw 是否有启动参数允许禁用/配置 token 认证。\n\n由于 Gateway 是二进制文件，用户无法修改其源码，所以我需要考虑其他方案：一个是在前端实现手动评分（油猴脚本已有），另一个是让 ws-proxy 通过 Control UI 获取有效的 Gateway token，第三是等待官方后续更新。\n\n我应该向用户说明这个限制，并提出这些替代方案。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n发现问题了！看日志：\n\n```\ncode=1008 reason=unauthorized: gateway token missing\n```\n\nGateway 是**二进制**，无法修改源码加白名单。\n\n**解决方案：**\n1. **你的油猴脚本** - 前端手动评分（已有）\n2. **让 ws-proxy 用正确的 token** - 需要从 Gateway 获取有效 token\n3. **等官方更新**\n\n你想怎么处理？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":42815,"output":528,"cacheRead":256,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43599,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775479781793,"responseId":"019d62d6eb0110e47e4ebdd404428cac"}}
