{"type":"message","id":"4b3cc366","parentId":"72fddddd","timestamp":"2026-04-06T12:53:05.834Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"ws-proxy 运行中。但 connections=0 意味着还没有客户端连接到它。ws-proxy 的连接 gateway 逻辑应该在有客户端连接时才建立。\n\n让我看看 gateway 日志有没有新的认证失败记录。同时让用户测试一下从油猴脚本连接。或者我手动发起一个 WebSocket 连接来触发 gateway 连接。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ed2e2ad23db34de9a9d75cf5","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"journalctl -u openclaw-gateway -n 10 --since \"1 minute ago\" 2>/dev/null | grep -i \"unauthorized\\|1008\\|ws-proxy\" || echo \"最近无相关日志\"","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":44102,"output":141,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44243,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775479983240,"responseId":"chatcmpl-5613cdc1-1be9-4aaa-b943-378accd9466a"}}
