{"type":"message","id":"76b24fc2","parentId":"a7e78b39","timestamp":"2026-04-06T12:54:30.314Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Gateway 的 challenge 响应格式可能需要包含 token。让我看看 Gateway 需要什么样的认证响应。\n\n由于是二进制 gateway，无法直接修改。但可以尝试修改 ws-proxy 的认证逻辑。\n\n根据一般的 WebSocket 认证流程，challenge 响应通常需要：\n1. 用 nonce + secret 生成响应\n2. 或者直接发送 token\n\n让我尝试修改 ws-proxy，让它在收到 challenge 时直接发送包含 token 的响应，而不是返回 nonce。\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d62db9c8c7ffddf27250e4de3cc95","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"if (msg.type === 'event' && msg.event === 'connect.challenge') {\n const nonce = msg.payload?.nonce;\n if (nonce) {\n // 直接发送 token 响应\n const token = process.env.OPENCLAW_TOKEN || '0da4fe1cb845fc8386105026ee6b941b288a2a4264a16ced';\n const response = JSON.stringify({\n type: 'event',\n event: 'auth',\n payload: { token }\n });\n this.gatewaySocket.send(response);\n log('info', `[${this.clientId}] Sent token auth`);\n return;\n }\n }","oldText":"if (msg.type === 'event' && msg.event === 'connect.challenge') {\n const nonce = msg.payload?.nonce;\n if (nonce) {\n // 生成响应\n const response = JSON.stringify({\n type: 'response',\n event: 'connect.challenge',\n payload: { nonce, response: nonce }\n });\n this.gatewaySocket.send(response);\n log('info', `[${this.clientId}] Sent challenge response`);\n return;\n }\n }"}],"path":"/home/ai/openclaw-router/ws-proxy.js"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":640,"output":384,"cacheRead":46208,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47232,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775480050047,"responseId":"019d62db815f03bb3c8852814b072738"}}
