{"type":"message","id":"36d1df7a","parentId":"c259f89e","timestamp":"2026-04-06T12:57:20.870Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_410636996fc54d06a0577f28","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"  const memoryStore = global.vectorMemory || null;\n  const result = await detectIntent(message, conversationId, memoryStore);\n  res.json(result);\n});\n\n// 对话路径拦截 - 意图判断 + 任务评分\napp.post('/api/chat/send', async (req, res, next) => {\n  const userMessage = req.body.message || req.body.text || req.body.content;\n  if (!userMessage) return next();\n  \n  const convId = req.body.conversationId || req.body.sessionId;\n  const memoryStore = global.vectorMemory || null;\n  \n  // 同步快速判断\n  const { isTask, confidence } = await detectIntent(userMessage, convId, memoryStore);\n  \n  if (isTask && confidence > 0.5) {\n    // 触发任务评分\n    const score = await computeFineScore(userMessage);\n    const plan = getExecutionPlan(score.totalScore, score.factors?.scaleIndex || 1);\n    console.log(`[Router] 检测到任务: \"${userMessage.slice(0,30)}...\" → 评分 ${score.totalScore} → ${plan.mode}`);\n    req.body.taskRouting = plan;\n  }\n  \n  next();\n});\n\n// 代理到 Gateway\napp.use('/', createProxyMiddleware({ \n  target: GATEWAY_URL, \n\n[8 more lines in file. Use offset=85 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775480240862}}
{"type":"message","id":"ba446779","parentId":"36d1df7a","timestamp":"2026-04-06T12:57:43.999Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我看到 Router 有一个 `/api/chat/send` 端点可以拦截消息进行评分，但问题是：\n\n1. 这个端点需要 WebSocket 前端改成通过 HTTP 发送到 Router (3102)，Router 再代理到 Gateway (3108)\n2. 或者油猴脚本可以模拟这个请求\n\n目前的 WebSocket 连接是直接到 Gateway (3108)，不经过 Router (3102)。\n\n让我检查油猴脚本能否直接调用这个 API 来自动评分。实际上油猴脚本已经是手动点击评分的方案了。\n\n另一个思路：能不能让所有 WebSocket 连接先到 Router，Router 再转发到 Gateway？这样 Router 可以拦截所有消息进行评分。\n\n但在 WebSocket 层面拦截需要 ws-proxy，这个我们已经试过走不通了。\n\n让我想想其他办法...\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nRouter 的 `/api/chat/send` 端点可以拦截评分，但问题是：\n\n1. Control UI 通过 WebSocket 直连 Gateway (3108)\n2. 不经过 Router (3102)\n3. WebSocket 拦截需要 ws-proxy（已失败）\n\n**如果能让 Control UI 改走 HTTP → Router → Gateway**，Router 就能自动评分。\n\n你能改 Control UI 的连接配置吗？或者有前端源码？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":5606,"output":247,"cacheRead":43520,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49373,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775480240871,"responseId":"019d62ddec1bd479643b2cb5a1461cdc"}}
