{"type":"message","id":"8d18fe08","parentId":"4b4c895b","timestamp":"2026-04-06T13:23:27.392Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问评分是什么机制，是不是动态的。我需要解释当前的评分机制。\n\n根据之前修改的 scoring.js，评分是静态的加权算法，不是动态学习的。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n当前是**静态加权算法**，不是动态的。\n\n```\n总分 = (instructionCount × 0.12 + codeLines × 0.08 + dependencyComplexity × 0.10 + \n       cpuIntensity × 0.10 + ioIntensity × 0.08 + networkIntensity × 0.12 + \n       estimatedDuration × 0.12 + scaleIndex × 0.28) × 20\n```\n\n每个因子靠正则匹配关键词（如 `docker`、`npm install`、`编译` 等）打分为 1-5 分。\n\n**不是动态的** — 不会根据历史数据自我学习。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":1432,"output":161,"cacheRead":51072,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":52665,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775481798935,"responseId":"019d62f58142279792c24d8e50290d97"}}
