{"type":"message","id":"b7a80be7","parentId":"126da2d5","timestamp":"2026-04-06T13:24:06.028Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问之前写的动态评分。之前有两个版本：\n\n1. 简洁版（动态评分）：\n```javascript\n// 加权总分（满分5+5+5=15，映射到0-100）\nconst total = (factors.instructionCount * 0.4 + factors.networkIntensity * 0.3 + factors.estimatedDuration * 0.3);\nconst totalScore = Math.min(100, Math.max(0, Math.round(total / 5 * 100)));\n```\n\n2. 精细版（当前用的）：8个因子，静态权重。\n\n用户之前说\"回到精细版\"，所以动态版被替换掉了。\n\n我需要回答：我之前提供了动态版和精细版，你选择了精细版。动态版更简单，只有3个因子。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n之前有两个版本：\n\n1. **动态版** — 3个因子，公式：`total = instructionCount×0.4 + networkIntensity×0.3 + estimatedDuration×0.3`，映射到 0-100\n\n2. **精细版** — 8个因子，当前在用\n\n你说\"回到精细版\"，所以现在用的是精细版（8个因子）。\n\n要切换回动态版吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":52715,"output":245,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":52960,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775481826250,"responseId":"chatcmpl-4619f0d5-2423-4cb7-b0b6-63506330e5c1"}}
