{"type":"message","id":"b53a4516","parentId":"b39fb35d","timestamp":"2026-04-06T13:48:00.737Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问 task_orchestrator 技能是干什么的。根据之前的对话，我知道它是任务评分和路由系统。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\ntask_orchestrator 是**任务评分和路由系统**，功能包括：\n\n1. **任务评分** — 分析任务复杂度，返回 0-100 分\n2. **路由决策** — 根据分数决定执行模式：\n   - DIRECT（≤20分）\n   - STEP_ARCHIVE（21-40分）\n   - SPAWN_SUBAGENT（41-60分）\n   - MEGA_TASK（>60分）\n3. **意图判断** — 检测用户消息是否是任务（置信度 > 0.5）\n\n当前运行在 **3102 端口**，你可以通过 `@p xxx` 手动触发评分。\n\n之前 ws-proxy 想用它做自动评分，但连不上 Gateway（认证问题），所以没成功。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":59280,"output":173,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":59453,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775483277291,"responseId":"chatcmpl-c7eaf6b6-d303-4cbe-b2d0-000dda4f1adb"}}
