{"type":"message","id":"58eb37a1","parentId":"f7dbbc97","timestamp":"2026-04-06T13:52:07.075Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"路径存在但是空的。现在我需要为用户设计一个每日检索伊朗战争新闻的工作流。根据 automation-workflows 技能的指导，我需要：1. 设计工作流（触发器、动作、错误处理）2. 选择工具（Zapier/Make/n8n）\n3. 提供具体实现\n\n让我创建一个工作流设计文档。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_46be2315e01c48a9899eb639","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/mnt/d/aafuzhi/xinjian/iran-war-news-workflow.md","content":"# 伊朗战争新闻每日检索工作流\n\n## 需求分析\n\n- **任务**: 每日自动检索伊朗战争相关新闻\n- **频率**: 每天一次\n- **目的**: 监控伊朗地区动态\n\n---\n\n## 工作流设计\n\n### 方案 A: Make (推荐)\n\n```\n触发器: 每天 8:00 (Schedule)\n\nActions:\n  Step 1: HTTP Request (GET news from Google News RSS)\n    URL: https://news.google.com/rss/search?q=Iran+war+OR+Iran+military+OR+伊朗+战争\n  \n  Step 2: Parse XML to JSON\n  \n  Step 3: Filter by date (today only)\n  \n  Step 4: Create Google Doc\n    Title: 伊朗战争新闻 - YYYY-MM-DD\n    Content: 解析后的新闻列表\n  \n  Step 5: Send Email (optional)\n    To: your@email.com\n    Subject: 今日伊朗战争新闻 - YYYY-MM-DD\n    Body: 新闻摘要\n```\n\n### 方案 B: n8n (自托管)\n\n```json\n{\n  \"nodes\": [\n    {\n      \"name\": \"Schedule\",\n      \"type\": \"n8n-nodes-base.scheduleTrigger\",\n      \"parameters\": {\n        \"rule\": {\"interval\": [{\"field\": \"hours\", \"hoursInterval\": 24}]}\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"name\": \"Fetch News\",\n      \"type\": \"n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest\",\n      \"parameters\": {\n        \"url\": \"https://news.google.com/rss/search?q=Iran+war+OR+伊朗+战争\",\n        \"method\": \"GET\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"name\": \"Parse RSS\",\n      \"type\": \"n8n-nodes-base.xml\",\n      \"parameters\": {}\n    },\n    {\n      \"name\": \"Save to File\",\n      \"type\": \"n8n-nodes-base.writeBinaryFile\",\n      \"parameters\": {\n        \"fileName\": \"/path/to/news-{{$now}}.json\",\n        \"data\": \"{{$json}}\"\n      }\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 工具对比\n\n| 工具 | 费用 | 难度 |\n|-----|------|------|\n| Make | $9-30/月 | 中等 |\n| n8n | 免费/自托管 | 较难 |\n| Zapier | $20+/月 | 简单 |\n\n---\n\n## 快速开始 (Make)\n\n1. 注册 [make.com](https://make.com)\n2. 创建新 Scenario\n3. 添加 Schedule 触发器 → 设置每天 8:00\n4. 添加 HTTP 模块 → URL 填 Google News RSS\n5. 添加 XML 模块解析\n6. 添加 Google Docs 模块创建文档\n7. 测试并启用\n\n---\n\n## 替代: 本地脚本方案\n\n如果不想用第三方工具，可以用 Python 脚本 + Cron：\n\n```python\n#!/usr/bin/env python3\nimport feedparser\nfrom datetime import datetime\n\nRSS_URL = \"https://news.google.com/rss/search?q=Iran+war+OR+Iran+military+OR+伊朗+战争\"\nOUTPUT_DIR = \"/mnt/d/aafuzhi/xinjian/\"\n\ndef fetch_news():\n    feed = feedparser.parse(RSS_URL)\n    today = datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d\")\n    \n    with open(f\"{OUTPUT_DIR}iran_news_{today}.txt\", \"w\", encoding=\"utf-8\") as f:\n        f.write(f\"# 伊朗战争新闻 - {today}\\n\\n\")\n        for entry in feed.entries[:10]:\n            f.write(f\"- [{entry.title}]({entry.link})\\n\")\n    \n    print(f\"已保存 {today} 的新闻\")\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    fetch_news()\n```\n\n设置 Cron 任务:\n```bash\n0 8 * * * /usr/bin/python3 /mnt/d/aafuzhi/xinjian/fetch_news.py\n```"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":62282,"output":946,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":63228,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775483512470,"responseId":"chatcmpl-70f13c4b-d91a-4786-a86b-e683471aa559"}}
