{"type":"message","id":"642a5fae","parentId":"9df4f951","timestamp":"2026-04-06T16:33:25.435Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问我正在做什么。我正在实现 v7.0 系统的剩余模块。已经完成了：\n1. 子代理进度上报 (progress-reporter.js) ✅\n\n还需要：\n2. 安全模块\n3. 效率优化\n4. 部署运维\n\n我在等待用户确认是否继续。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n正在实现 v7.0 系统模块，已完成：\n\n- 评分因子 → scoring-v7.js ✅\n- 超大任务执行器 → mega-executor.js ✅\n- 上下文保护 → context-protector.js ✅\n- **子代理进度上报 → progress-reporter.js** ✅ (刚写完)\n\n剩余：\n- 安全模块\n- 效率优化\n- 部署运维\n\n继续？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":81630,"output":143,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":81773,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775493202227,"responseId":"chatcmpl-3dc22e95-518f-4cef-a5d4-f74578dbd677"}}
