{"type":"message","id":"b341249a","parentId":"031a5a1f","timestamp":"2026-04-06T17:14:44.779Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"\n用户问接入OpenClaw执行流程有没有实现全自动。需要我检查当前架构：\n1. 评分模块(v7)已集成到Router 3102\n2. Router会拦截 `/api/chat/send` 请求，自动评分\n3. 但是 Control UI 目前是直接连 Gateway 3108，不经过 Router\n4. 所以自动评分还没生效，需要让 Control UI 走 Router 3102\n\n需要如实回答：\n✅ Router 内部自动评分逻辑已实现\n⚠️ 但是流程没有全打通，因为 Control UI 直连 Gateway\n需要改 Control UI 的 API 地址为 Router 3102 才能全自动\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"还差最后一步：让 Control UI 走 Router 的 3102 端口才能完全自动化。\n\n**当前流程状态：**\n| 模块 | 状态 |\n|-----|------|\n| Router 自动评分逻辑 | ✅ 已实现（收到消息自动打分） |\n| Control UI → Gateway 连接 | ❌ 直连 3108，不经过 Router |\n| 自动评分生效 | ❌ 没有拦截到消息 |\n\n**要完全全自动需要：**\n修改 Control UI 的 API 地址从 `http://localhost:3108` 改为 `http://localhost:3102`\nRouter 会自动拦截所有消息进行评分，然后转发给 Gateway。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"doubao-seed-2.0-pro","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775495676171,"responseId":"0217754956752360076f3f588c303a7ab8265369cf81576a85e3d"}}
