{"type":"message","id":"e5d64ca3","parentId":"0e14660c","timestamp":"2026-04-06T17:15:21.516Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"\n用户现在问的是能不能做到评分接入OpenClaw执行流程全自动，以及怎么做到。首先我需要明确告诉用户可以做到，然后分步骤解释怎么做。\n首先，当然可以做到。然后分两种方案：一种是改前端（控制UI的地址），另一种是改端口转发（把3108端口转发给Router，由Router再转发给Gateway的其他端口）。\n需要先评分，按照用户要求，以@p开头会自动评分，这里我需要调用评分API，然后回答问题。\n首先调用评分接口，任务是\"接入OpenClaw的执行流程实现全自动评分\"，然后告诉用户可以做到，给出方案。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_g1yqiequ4m8rn9ryz2dn3qyi","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s -X POST http://127.0.0.1:3102/api/task -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d '{\"taskSpec\":\"接入OpenClaw的执行流程实现全自动评分\"}' | jq '.score, .routing.mode'","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"doubao-seed-2.0-pro","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775495713654,"responseId":"021775495712932d619db30bd0c9858e230a26bb16935251076ad"}}
