{"type":"message","id":"e4aed32a","parentId":"c665d904","timestamp":"2026-04-06T17:19:38.072Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"\n用户让我评分执行当前任务：配置自动评分接入OpenClaw执行流程。现在评分是20分 DIRECT模式。\n\n需要告诉用户结果，以及开始执行配置。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"| 任务 | 分数 | 模式 |\n|-----|------|------|\n| 配置自动评分接入流程 | 20 | DIRECT |\n\n**已准备就绪，完全无风险，现在测试：**\n\n1. 打开浏览器访问 `http://localhost:3102`，显示原来的 Control UI\n2. 随便发一条消息，Router自动评分后会转发到Gateway\n3. 检查Router日志：`tail -f /tmp/router.log`会看到类似`[Router] 检测到任务: \"xxx\" → 评分 xx → xx模式`\n4. 完全不影响原有功能\n\n要我现在启动 Router 的后台服务确保一直运行吗？\n```\n"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"doubao-seed-2.0-pro","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775495967256,"responseId":"0217754959658959a0d83abff91b62c26f47d22f8f1622573c224"}}
