{"type":"message","id":"676eddc8","parentId":"f9556cf4","timestamp":"2026-04-06T17:21:53.659Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"\n用户想要让 Router 服务开机自启动。我需要创建一个 systemd service 文件，然后启用它，这样开机就会自动运行。\n\n先创建服务文件：\n1. 服务名称可以叫 openclaw-router.service\n2. 配置启动命令和路径\n3. 设置自动重启\n4. 安装并启用服务\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1ht2om8sirl5uob561zjkt4u","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/openclaw-router.service","content":"[Unit]\nDescription=OpenClaw Task Orchestrator Router v7\nAfter=network.target\n\n[Service]\nType=simple\nUser=ai\nWorkingDirectory=/home/ai/openclaw-router\nExecStart=/home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/bin/node openclaw-router.js\nRestart=always\nRestartSec=5\nEnvironment=NODE_ENV=production\nEnvironment=OPENCLAW_GATEWAY=http://127.0.0.1:18789\nEnvironment=ROUTER_PORT=3102\n\n[Install]\nWantedBy=default.target\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"doubao-seed-2.0-pro","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775496106617,"responseId":"021775496105485289ee8f5cd43d8cc040debd1abd108ae62eec8"}}
