{"type":"message","id":"23b24787","parentId":"2c5c1258","timestamp":"2026-04-06T17:22:18.983Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"\n刚才的systemd配置有问题，我们用简单的方式自启动就可以了。最简单的方式是把启动命令放到用户的rc.local或者bashrc里，或者使用pm2来管理进程，更简单稳定。\n\n用户想要自启动，最简单的方式是使用pm2（node进程管理器），比systemd更适合node应用。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"systemd 配置有点问题，我用更简单的方式配置自启动，保证不会影响 OpenClaw：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_mbyiln04pv2lpscvxm4juee3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 安装pm2（node进程管理器）\nnpm install -g pm2 -q\ncd /home/ai/openclaw-router\npm2 start openclaw-router.js --name openclaw-router\npm2 save\npm2 startup\n","timeout":30}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"doubao-seed-2.0-pro","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775496127844,"responseId":"021775496127012289ee8f5cd43d8cc040debd1abd108aef2007a"}}
