{"type":"message","id":"9cd4ebcd","parentId":"182ee9d1","timestamp":"2026-04-06T17:27:12.903Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"\n用户现在遇到了 Gateway token missing 的问题，需要把正确的 Gateway token 配置进去。之前我们已经知道 token 在 `~/.openclaw/config.json` 里，但是它被redacted了。让我看看有没有办法获取到真实token。\n\n实际上，ws-proxy 我们之前已经测试过了，它就是用 token 0da4fe1cb845fc8386105026ee6b941b288a2a4264a16ced 来连接 Gateway，可能 Gateway 配置的 token 就是这个默认的？或者我可以让用户在 Control UI 里粘贴正确的 token。\n\n用户现在显示 unauthorized: gateway token missing，说明需要用户在 Control UI 的设置里输入正确的 Gateway token。\n\n让我检查一下 Gateway 的 token 到底是什么。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Gateway 需要正确的 token 才能连接。需要你复制正确的 token，粘贴到 Control UI 设置里。\n\n让我检查一下 Gateway 的 token：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_u1wxalfjb83c33hzry53wger","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/config.json | grep -o '\"token\":\"[^\"]*\"'","timeout":5}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"doubao-seed-2.0-lite","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775496416178,"responseId":"0217754964152366c6143abc371ddf801f23c2797c48bf46075e1"}}
