{"type":"message","id":"2cd44e12","parentId":"5de176b9","timestamp":"2026-04-06T17:55:05.558Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-04-07 01:55 GMT+8] ai@ai:~$ tail -f /tmp/router.log\n[Router] Task scored: 20 → DIRECT\n[Router] Task scored: 20 → DIRECT\n[Router] Task scored: 20 → DIRECT\n[Router] Task scored: 45 → SPAWN_SUBAGENT\n[Intent] msg=\"改 Gateway 源码 - 加认证白名单\" syncScore=0 contextBonus=0 memoryBonus=0 finalScore=0 isTask=false\n[Router] Task scored: 20 → DIRECT\n[Router] Task scored: 31 → STEP_ARCHIVE\n[Router] Task scored: 20 → DIRECT\n[Router] Task scored: 20 → DIRECT\n[Router] Task scored: 20 → DIRECT\n这里没显示评分了啊"}],"timestamp":1775498105539}}
{"type":"message","id":"5fceb537","parentId":"2cd44e12","timestamp":"2026-04-06T17:55:17.326Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"\n用户现在发日志给我看，说现在没显示 \"检测到任务: ...\" 这句话了，只显示 \"Task scored: ...\"。\n\n让我看一下代码：\n- 自动检测到任务的时候，应该输出：`console.log(\\`[Router] 检测到任务: \"${userMessage.slice(0,30)}...\" → 评分 ${score.totalScore} → ${plan.mode}\\`);`\n- 然后 `Task scored: ${score.totalScore} → ${plan.mode}` 是手动调用 `/api/task` 输出的\n\n用户说现在只看到 `Task scored: 20 → DIRECT` 没有看到 \"检测到任务...\"\n\n这说明 `app.post('/api/chat/send')` 这个拦截端点没有被触发？为什么？\n\n因为用户访问的是 ws:// 直接连接，不是 HTTP POST /api/chat/send。拦截端点只工作在 HTTP 路径，WebSocket 消息走的是直接代理，不会经过 /api/chat/send 路由。\n\n所以意图检测和自动评分只在 HTTP API 请求时工作，WebSocket 消息没有经过这个路由，所以不会自动评分。\n\n我需要修改 Router 让 WebSocket 消息也能被拦截评分。这个需要增加 WebSocket 消息拦截，因为原来的 http-proxy-middleware 只代理 HTTP，WebSocket 消息是直接透传的，所以无法处理。\n\n需要增加 WebSocket 消息拦截和处理，让每个消息都能经过意图检测和评分。\n\n我需要修改 openclaw-router.js，增加 WebSocket 消息拦截逻辑。\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"发现问题了！HTTP 请求会走 `/api/chat/send` 拦截路由自动评分，但 WebSocket 消息直接透传给 Gateway，不会被拦截评分。\n\n需要给 Router 添加 WebSocket 消息拦截，这样每条 WebSocket 消息都会自动检测意图+评分。现在修复：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_esoblc8p49a33srxkfh4v6le","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/openclaw-router/openclaw-router.js","edits":[{"oldText":"// WebSocket Upgrade处理\napp.on('upgrade', proxy.upgrade);","newText":"// WebSocket Upgrade处理 + 消息拦截\nconst server = require('http').createServer(app);\n\nserver.on('upgrade', (request, socket, head) => {\n  // 拦截消息进行自动评分\n  proxy.upgrade(request, socket, head);\n  \n  // 监听消息，自动评分\n  socket.on('data', (data) => {\n    try {\n      const msg = JSON.parse(data.toString());\n      if (msg.type === 'message' && msg.content) {\n        const userMessage = msg.content;\n        // 异步检测意图和评分\n        (async () => {\n          const { isTask, confidence } = await detectIntent(userMessage);\n          if (isTask && confidence > 0.5) {\n            const score = await computeFineScore(userMessage);\n            const plan = getExecutionPlan(score.totalScore, score.factors?.scaleIndex || 1);\n            console.log(`[Router] 检测到任务: \"${userMessage.slice(0,30)}...\" → 评分 ${score.totalScore} → ${plan.mode}`);\n            // 记录指标\n            metrics.counter('openclaw_tasks_total').inc();\n            metrics.counter('openclaw_task_routes', { mode: plan.mode }).inc();\n            healthChecker.recordTask(plan.mode, score.totalScore);\n          }\n        })();\n      }\n    } catch(e) {\n      // 解析失败不影响转发\n    }\n  });\n});\n\nserver.listen(PORT, () => console.log(`Router on ${PORT} → ${GATEWAY_URL}`));\nconsole.log('[Router] Task Orchestrator v3.0 ready - scoring enabled - intent detection enabled');"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"doubao-seed-2.0-lite","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775498105556,"responseId":"021775498105546fadef930ee560a642a71bddf4d1e9937258d0f"}}
