{"type":"message","id":"812e4206","parentId":"95ab93c6","timestamp":"2026-04-06T18:06:54.743Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"还有问题，现在看代码，我之前改成了 server.listen，但还需要让 app 的监听也改过来。我需要完整修复：\n\n原来的代码：\n```javascript\n// WebSocket Upgrade处理\nconst server = require('http').createServer(app);\n\nserver.on('upgrade', (request, socket, head) => {\n  // 拦截消息进行自动评分\n  proxy.upgrade(request, socket, head);\n  \n  // 监听消息，自动评分\n  socket.on('data', (data) => {\n    try {\n      const msg = JSON.parse(data.toString());\n      if (msg.type === 'message' && msg.content) {\n        const userMessage = msg.content;\n        // 异步检测意图和评分\n        (async () => {\n          const { isTask, confidence } = await detectIntent(userMessage);\n          if (isTask && confidence > 0.5) {\n            const score = await computeFineScore(userMessage);\n            const plan = getExecutionPlan(score.totalScore, score.factors?.scaleIndex || 1);\n            console.log(`[Router] 检测到任务: \"${userMessage.slice(0,30)}...\" → 评分 ${score.totalScore} → ${plan.mode}`);\n            // 记录指标\n            metrics.counter('openclaw_tasks_total').inc();\n            metrics.counter('openclaw_task_routes', { mode: plan.mode }).inc();\n            healthChecker.recordTask(plan.mode, score.totalScore);\n          }\n        })();\n      }\n    } catch(e) {\n      // 解析失败不影响转发\n    }\n  });\n});\n\nserver.listen(PORT, () => console.log(`Router on ${PORT} → ${GATEWAY_URL}`));\nconsole.log('[Router] Task Orchestrator v3.0 ready - scoring enabled - intent detection enabled');\n```\n\n刚才我把 app.listen 注释掉了，但需要保留 server.listen。现在修复：","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"发现问题了，刚才注释错了。重新修复：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_t8gfe0sy14q4aw6cp95s9oqf","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/openclaw-router/openclaw-router.js","limit":30,"offset":110}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"doubao-seed-2.0-lite","usage":{"inpu