{"type":"message","id":"3183d683","parentId":"e7fd3acb","timestamp":"2026-04-06T18:12:39.137Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说还是没有日志输出，我需要思考为什么。\n\n问题分析：\n1. Router 已经监听 3102 ✅\n2. WebSocket 连接已经建立 ✅\n3. 用户发送消息后，Router 的 socket.on('data') 应该被触发，应该打印日志，但日志里没有\n\n可能的原因：\n1. WebSocket 消息的格式不对，我的解析错误\n2. JSON 解析失败，被 catch 吞掉了，看不到日志\n3. 用户刷新页面后，新的 Router 进程没有收到消息，因为旧进程还在\n\n让我检查代码，看看问题在哪里。\n\n我之前的代码：\n```javascript\nserver.on('upgrade', (request, socket, head) => {\n  // 拦截消息进行自动评分\n  proxy.upgrade(request, socket, head);\n  \n  // 监听消息，自动评分\n  socket.on('data', (data) => {\n    try {\n      const msg = JSON.parse(data.toString());\n      if (msg.type === 'message' && msg.content) {\n        const userMessage = msg.content;\n        // ... 评分\n      }\n    } catch(e) {\n      // 解析失败不影响转发\n    }\n  });\n});\n```\n\n问题可能是：\n- Gateway 已经完成 upgrade 握手后，socket 是加密的？不，应该是明文 WebSocket\n- 我的代码在 proxy.upgrade 之后添加 data 监听器，会不会太晚？\n- 实际上 proxy 已经接管了 socket，我的监听器没有加上？\n\n更好的方式：应该在 proxy 处理之前先接管 socket，保存原始数据，然后再转给 proxy。或者我需要自己解析整个连接。\n\n让我修复代码，把监听放在 proxy 处理之前，并且修改监听方式。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"找到了问题！WebSocket 消息监听加错位置了。proxy 接管了 socket，我的监听器没生效。\n\n我修复代码：\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_erpbifpb3notpdskjeyf2qnl","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/openclaw-router/openclaw-router.js","edits":[{"oldText":"// WebSocket Upgrade处理 + 消息拦截\nconst server = require('http').createServer(app);\n\nserver.on('upgrade', (request, socket, head) => {\n  // 拦截消息进行自动评分\n  proxy.upgrade(request, socket, head);\n  \n  // 监听消息，自动评分\n  socket.on('data', (data) => {\n    try {\n      const msg = JSON.parse(data.toString());\n      if (msg.type === 'message' && msg.content) {\n        const userMessage = msg.content;\n        // 异步检测意图和评分\n        (async () => {\n          const { isTask, confidence } = await detectIntent(userMessage);\n          if (isTask && confidence > 0.5) {\n            const score = await computeFineScore(userMessage);\n            const plan = getExecutionPlan(score.totalScore, score.factors?.scaleIndex || 1);\n            console.log(`[Router] 检测到任务: \"${userMessage.slice(0,30)}...\" → 评分 ${score.totalScore} → ${plan.mode}`);\n            // 记录指标\n            metrics.counter('openclaw_tasks_total').inc();\n            metrics.counter('openclaw_task_routes', { mode: plan.mode }).inc();\n            healthChecker.recordTask(plan.mode, score.totalScore);\n          }\n        })();\n      }\n    } catch(e) {\n      // 解析失败不影响转发\n    }\n  });\n});\n\nserver.listen(PORT, () => console.log(`Router on ${PORT} → ${GATEWAY_URL}`));\nconsole.log('[Router] Task Orchestrator v3.0 ready - scoring enabled - intent detection enabled');","newText":"// WebSocket Upgrade处理 + 消息拦截\nconst server = require('http').createServer(app);\n\nserver.on('upgrade', (request, socket, head) => {\n  // 保存原始socket，添加监听器\n  const originalSocket = socket;\n  \n  // 包裹socket，捕获所有data事件\n  const originalEmit = socket.emit;\n  socket.emit = function(event, ...args) {\n    if (event === 'data') {\n      const data = args[0];\n      try {\n        const msg = JSON.parse(data.toString());\n        if (msg.type === 'message' && msg.content) {\n          const userMessage = msg.content;\n          // 异步检测意图和评分\n          (async () => {\n            const { isTask, confidence } = await detectIntent(userMessage);\n            if (isTask && confidence > 0.5) {\n              const score = await computeFineScore(userMessage);\n              const plan = getExecutionPlan(score.totalScore, score.factors?.scaleIndex || 1);\n              console.log(`[Router] 检测到任务: \"${userMessage.slice(0,30)}...\" → 评分 ${score.totalScore} → ${plan.mode}`);\n              // 记录指标\n              metrics.counter('openclaw_tasks_total').inc();\n              metrics.counter('openclaw_task_routes', { mode: plan.mode }).inc();\n              healthChecker.recordTask(plan.mode, score.totalScore);\n            }\n          })();\n        }\n      } catch(e) {\n        // 解析失败不影响转发\n      }\n    }\n    return originalEmit.call(this, event, ...args);\n  };\n  \n  proxy.upgrade(request, socket, head);\n});\n\nserver.listen(PORT, () => console.log(`Router on ${PORT} → ${GATEWAY_URL}`));\nconsole.log('[Router] Task Orchestrator v3.0 ready - scoring enabled - intent detection enabled');"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"doubao-seed-2.0-lite","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775499141756,"responseId":"02177549914109600bcc3116dfc56b9203b01425516f61b620225"}}
