{"type":"message","id":"b1822e60","parentId":"81f8bc0a","timestamp":"2026-04-06T18:17:45.331Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-04-07 02:14 GMT+8] ai@ai:~$ tail -f /tmp/router.log\n errno: -98,\n syscall: 'listen',\n address: '::',\n port: 3102\n}\n\nNode.js v22.22.1\n[Security] No whitelist config, using defaults\n[Router] Task Orchestrator v3.0 ready - scoring enabled - intent detection enabled\nRouter on 3102 → http://127.0.0.1:3108\n还是没有"}],"timestamp":1775499465315}}
{"type":"message","id":"42a70c0c","parentId":"b1822e60","timestamp":"2026-04-06T18:18:16.895Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户一直说\"还是没有\"，这说明WebSocket消息拦截仍然没有生效。让我再深入分析一下问题。\n\n查看一下当前的日志，只有启动信息，没有\"检测到任务\"或\"Task scored\"的记录。这意味着要么：\n1. WebSocket连接没有建立成功（用户没连接）\n2. 用户连接了但没发消息\n3. WebSocket消息拦截代码还是没抓到消息\n\n让我先检查一下Gateway连接状态。从之前日志看，用户应该已经成功连接了Gateway（WebSocket connected）。那么问题就在我的拦截代码。\n\n我的代码修改了socket.emit来捕获'data'事件，但可能需要更早地介入。实际上，http-proxy-middleware可能内部处理了WebSocket，导致我的emit覆盖没生效。\n\n我需要一个更直接的方法：直接使用WebSocket服务器来拦截消息。可以用ws库创建一个WebSocket服务器，然后代理到Gateway。\n\n但这样改动较大。也许可以先测试一下我的拦截代码是否正确运行。让我检查一下日志有没有任何错误，或者我可以在catch块中添加日志。\n\n我需要修改代码，在catch中打印错误，以便看到JSON解析是否失败。\n\n让我修改代码，在catch中添加日志，看看消息格式是否正确。\n\n另外，我应该检查WebSocket消息的实际格式。Control UI发送的消息可能是二进制数据或不同格式。\n\n让我修改代码，先打印原始数据，看看它长什么样。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_PDOi7w7tjBY6HSqf7FLev26D","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/openclaw-router/openclaw-router.js","edits":[{"oldText":"        // 包裹socket，捕获所有data事件\n        const originalEmit = socket.emit;\n        socket.emit = function(event, ...args) {\n          if (event === 'data') {\n            const data = args[0];\n            try {\n              const msg = JSON.parse(data.toString());\n              if (msg.type === 'message' && msg.content) {\n                const userMessage = msg.content;\n                // 异步检测意图和评分\n                (async () => {\n                  const { isTask, confidence } = await detectIntent(userMessage);\n                  if (isTask && confidence > 0.5) {\n                    const score = await computeFineScore(userMessage);\n                    const plan = getExecutionPlan(score.totalScore, score.factors?.scaleIndex || 1);\n                    console.log(`[Router] 检测到任务: \\\"${userMessage.slice(0,30)}...\\\" → 评分 ${score.totalScore} → ${plan.mode}`);\n                    // 记录指标\n                    metrics.counter('openclaw_tasks_total').inc();\n                    metrics.counter('openclaw_task_routes', { mode: plan.mode }).inc();\n                    healthChecker.recordTask(plan.mode, score.totalScore);\n                  }\n                })();\n              }\n            } catch(e) {\n              // 解析失败不影响转发\n            }\n          }\n          return originalEmit.call(this, event, ...args);\n        };","newText":"        // 包裹socket，捕获所有data事件\n        const originalEmit = socket.emit;\n        socket.emit = function(event, ...args) {\n          if (event === 'data') {\n            const data = args[0];\n            // 调试：打印原始数据前50字节\n            const raw = data.toString();\n            if (raw.length > 0) {\n              console.log(`[Router] WebSocket raw data (${raw.length} bytes): ${raw.slice(0, 50)}${raw.length > 50 ? '...' : ''}`);\n            }\n            try {\n              const msg = JSON.parse(raw);\n              console.log(`[Router] WebSocket parsed: type=${msg.type}, content=${msg.content ? 'yes' : 'no'}`);\n              if (msg.type === 'message' && msg.content) {\n                const userMessage = msg.content;\n                console.log(`[Router] WebSocket message: ${userMessage.slice(0,30)}...`);\n                // 异步检测意图和评分\n                (async () => {\n                  const { isTask, confidence } = await detectIntent(userMessage);\n                  console.log(`[Router] Intent result: isTask=${isTask}, confidence=${confidence}`);\n                  if (isTask && confidence > 0.5) {\n                    const score = await computeFineScore(userMessage);\n                    const plan = getExecutionPlan(score.totalScore, score.factors?.scaleIndex || 1);\n                    console.log(`[Router] 检测到任务: \\\"${userMessage.slice(0,30)}...\\\" → 评分 ${score.totalScore} → ${plan.mode}`);\n                    // 记录指标\n                    metrics.counter('openclaw_tasks_total').inc();\n                    metrics.counter('openclaw_task_routes', { mode: plan.mode }).inc();\n                    healthChecker.recordTask(plan.mode, score.totalScore);\n                  }\n                })();\n              }\n            } catch(e) {\n              console.log(`[Router] WebSocket parse error: ${e.message}`);\n              // 解析失败不影响转发\n            }\n          }\n          return originalEmit.call(this, event, ...args);\n        };"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":53421,"output":1488,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":54909,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775499465329,"responseId":"e21a7e41-8a92-4bd3-9eff-1b3b9ae25d1b"}}
