{"type":"message","id":"41d09bec","parentId":"7e715c22","timestamp":"2026-04-06T18:19:14.792Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Router正在运行。现在让我检查最新的日志，看看是否有调试输出。应该已经重启了，因为进程ID变了。现在用户刷新页面重新连接，发送消息，就能看到调试日志。让我告诉用户这个情况。现在修复完成并已重启。让用户刷新页面，重新连接，然后发送消息，就能在日志中看到详细的调试信息，包括WebSocket消息的原始格式。这样我就能知道为什么拦截失败了。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ **已添加调试日志**，现在重启完成。\n\n**请操作：**\n1. **刷新浏览器** `http://localhost:3102/chat?session=main`\n2. **重新连接** Gateway (token: `0da4fe1cb845fc8386105026ee6b941b288a2a4264a16ced`)\n3. **发送一条消息**\n4. **看终端日志** `tail -f /tmp/router.log`\n\n日志现在会显示：\n```\n[Router] WebSocket raw data: ... (原始数据)\n[Router] WebSocket parsed: type=..., content=...\n[Router] Intent result: isTask=..., confidence=...\n[Router] 检测到任务: \"...消息...\" → 评分 xx → 模式 xx\n```\n\n这样就能看到为什么之前没生效了。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":217,"output":354,"cacheRead":57472,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":58043,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775499548893,"responseId":"1143fd26-70b0-4156-b4d3-33cd4e7e55a8"}}
